  (text "LIGHTRAIL AI NCE - NEURAL COMPUTING ENGINE\nMain System Schematic\n\nSystem Architecture:\n• LR-GEN3-NPU 5nm Processor (256 cores, 1.5 TFLOPS FP32 @ 2.4 GHz)\n• 12x 16GB HBM3 Memory Stacks (192GB total, 256 GB/s bandwidth)\n• 12-Phase PWM Power Delivery (225W typical, 275W peak)\n• Dual PCIe x16 Form Factor with 40mm Cooling Fans\n• Complete Temperature Monitoring & Thermal Management\n\nSubsystems:\n1. Power Delivery Network (PDN) - 0.9V Core, 1.2V Memory, Auxiliary Rails\n2. PCIe Interface - Gen4 x16 with Input Protection\n3. HBM3 Memory Subsystem - 12 Stacks with Decoupling\n4. Clock Distribution - 27MHz TCXO → On-chip PLL → 2.4 GHz\n5. Thermal Management - Dual Fans, Temperature Sensors, PWM Control\n6. Debug Interface - JTAG TAP with Boundary Scan\n7. Power Sequencing - Soft-start, Ramp Control, Fault Protection\n\nSee detailed schematics in separate sheets for each subsystem."
    (at 60 45.72) (effects (font (size 3.81 3.81) (thickness 0.254)) (justify left)) (uuid "text1"))

